column5: Appreciate the info on Saskatoon. Our travel plans have changed, will be going thru Price Albert instead. Anybody able to help us in buyinga pound or two of leeches??? Phone # would be great so we can call ahead if possible.

Are you sure you are not going through Saskatoon? From where are you coming? What I mean is, to get to PA from the South without going through Saskatoon is generally going off the beaten path. derrek."Just because I'm paranoid doesn't mean they're not out to get me."
